個人認為未學過haskell, 都唔算試晒FP<img src="/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif" class="hkgmoji" /><img src="/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif" class="hkgmoji" /><br />
<br />
講真我都只係學到一半，都未算熟，冇寫production code 嘅機會，但都有用過佢嚟寫啲open source<br />
<br />
<a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/postcss-sparrow-clamp-fallback" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npmjs.com%2Fpackage%2Fpostcss-sparrow-clamp-fallback&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kypR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=9ef7ebc7" data-auto-link target="_blank">https://www.npmjs.com/package/postcss-sparrow-clamp-fallback</a><br />
<br />
typeclass 嘅好處係，可以用type constraint 去modify 一個function, 等佢你可以用一個 fn 名handle 唔同type 嘅input, 而唔係寫幾個唔同名嘅fn. 重點都係想reuse 啲code<br />
<br />
如果冇typeclass 你又想做啲type specific 嘅generic fn, 你會做好多fn, 之後每個個名都唔同<br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type="">const strToInt = () =&gt; {
//...
}

const arrToInt = () =&gt; {
//...
}

const objToInt = () =&gt; {
//...
}</code></pre><br />
<br />
如果有type class, define 完instance 之後， 你只係需要call <code>toInt</code>, 同一個fn 名就可以有晒對應唔同type 嘅behavior<br />
<pre><code data-type="">class ToInt a where
  toInt :: a -&gt; Int

instance StrToInt :: ToInt String
  toInt :: String -&gt; Int


instance ArrToInt :: forall a. ToInt Array a
  toInt :: Array a -&gt; Int
</code></pre>

